07/11/2010
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- Police in Republika Srpska and the Federation of BiH detained 14 people in an anti-drug operation Friday (November 5th) after searching more than 20 locations across the country. 
The police action was part of a regional operation that started last year in BiH and Croatia, police spokesperson Mirna Solaja said. 
(RTRS, BHRT, AP - 05/11/10)
